import Mathlib

open Complex

/-- Schwarz lemma: if f : ùîª ‚Üí ùîª is holomorphic (differentiable on the unit disk) and f(0)=0,
then |f z| ‚â§ |z| for all z in the unit disk. -/
theorem schwarz_lemma {f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ}
  (h_diff : DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f {z : ‚ÑÇ | abs z < 1})
  (h_map : ‚àÄ z, abs z < 1 ‚Üí abs (f z) < 1)
  (h0 : f 0 = 0) : ‚àÄ z, abs (f z) ‚â§ abs z := by sorry
